!Bxf7 {[%fen "rn1qkbnr/pp2pp1b/2p4p/4N2p/2B4P/6N1/PPPP1PP1/R1B1K2R w KQkq - 0 2"]} {The queen is strong, but mate is better. Black is the one in trouble here! What do you think White played?}
